title: QUE PROCEDE?

embed.description: Riot Games Support will help you with any questions or problems you have with League of Legends. From tech to account to game problems, Riot Games is here to help!

body: Ya mande ticket al soporte de nuevo como la vez anterior, en serio siguen dejando jugar a esa gente?

replies.body: Nosotros no vemos el ticket dentro de tu cuenta, voxero nabo.
